desc_long							评测						“Yeah, this game throws a few curveballs your way. It's got solid variety and just a good feel to the game when you play it.”Touch Arcade“Overall though, Darthy is a sharp little action game that platforming fans should try out.”4/5 Rock n Roll – 148 Apps“old-skool influenced 2D platformer with decent controls, a great look”Pocket Gamer												关于这款游戏							DARTHY wakes up in the hospital and soon finds out he must release the souls of the robots imprisoned in the Gold Doubloons (Gold Coins) by the Giant Space Pirates. Help DARTHY Roll, Bounce, Crash, Fly, and Die to free the unfortunate souls.DARTHY is a Simple Pixel Platformer based on old school mechanics. Made with my kids Kaleb & Jeya play testing.FEATURES◉ 10+ Buildings w/ Old School Checkpoints ◉ Pixel Art ◉ Double Jump & Fireball◉ Collect Coins to help the Robots ◉ Real-time physics◉ Prepare to die. A lot!◉ Security Ballz https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=399054255						
